zm Urban Downtown Final


Well guys. This is it. I've been working on this map for a while now. And the job is done. This is the final version. It's a nice downtown with a bank, a gas station, a movie theater, and a lot more.

Terrorists are trying to explode the city hall. Disable the bomb and kill all those bastards to save the day.

Spawn Points: 64

Thanks to:

A special thanks to the guys at ICC server, specialy Sandfly. This project would not be possible, with this quality, without you guys.
